@steveblackmon Again this stuff is really cool.

There are some doc fixes and I was wondering whether there's a problem with the json-schema encoding the IDs as integer/long but this is looking pretty good.

Also, AFAICT `ListSerializer` relies on the `PartType` class from Juneau that's in an unpublished snapshot. Are you hoping that the snapshot or a release will be published before this merges?
